flowRoot.flowPara: Pricing: $100-150 for full written article/review; $40 for brief post; $25 for social media mention. Advertisements & sponsorships negotiable. Sliding scale pricing available for non-profits & individuals.
Please note: Spoonie Living will not publish follow links in exchange for money or products. All sponsored posts will be tagged as such.
Followers view articles on their "dashboard"; this does not contribute to the pageview count unless they click through to view the article on the blog. Metrics for Tumblr views are not available.
Pageview count does not include article views via Tumblr "dashboard." Articles are viewed at a much higher rate.
Each post is tweeted to Spoonie Living's Twitter account.
Spoonie Living publishes daily articles that provide specific, actionable resources for all forms of chronic illness and disability, including mental illness, learning disabilities, and addiction.

text.tspan: Please direct inquiries to Diane Murray at contact@spoonieliving.com
